{
  "chapter": 45,
  "chapter_summary": "第四十五回\"前尘往事\"讲述郭大路与燕七洞房花烛夜的故事。二人新婚之夜虽略显生疏，却很快恢复了往日的调侃与默契。燕七终于向郭大路坦白了自己的女子身份，并透露此前的种种考验——包括秘屋的秘密、龙王庙的勇气——都是南宫丑及朋友们对郭大路的品行测试。二人回忆起南宫丑的坚韧与神驼子、金罗汉等人对他超越生死的忠诚友情，感慨伟大人格的力量。次日启程回富贵山庄途中，郭大路偶遇一位沦为乞丐的旧情人。妇人因嫉妒燕七的幸福而撒泼纠缠，燕七以一条金链子巧妙化解僵局。事后燕七透露那并非郭大路原物，而是梅兰所赠的贺礼。郭大路深深感激妻子的了解与体谅，二人携手踏上归途。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "我要睡了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "今天你怎么没有要我出去？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你少说几句，我就睡着了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "有我在屋里，你也睡得着？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你……你不是别人。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "不是别人是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你是个大头鬼。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "奇怪奇怪，你怎么会嫁给我这大头鬼的？我记得你以前好像说过，就算天下的男人全都死光了，也不会嫁给我。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你……你……你想干什么？",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "我想咬你一口。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "奇怪，真奇怪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "又奇怪什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "你身上为什么一点也不臭？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "你知道我现在想什么？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "我想起了很多奇怪的事，但最想的，还是个烧得又红又烂的大蹄膀。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你能不能说你是在想着我？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "不能。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "不能？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "因为我怕把你一口吞下去。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "你这老婆我得来可真不容易，若是吞下去，岂非没有了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "没有岂非正好再去找一个。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "找谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "譬如说……酸梅汤。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "不行，她太酸，而且她喜欢的是你。现在我才知道，那天你不要她，她为什么一点也不生气了……那天你想必已告诉她，你也跟她一样，是个女人。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "我若是男人，我就要她了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "你为什么一直不肯告诉我，你是个女人呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "谁叫你是个瞎子，别人都看出来了，就是你看不出来。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "你要告诉我的就是这个秘密？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "你为什么一定要等到我快死的时候，才肯告诉我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "因为……因为我怕你不要我……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "我们好好的聊聊，不许你乱动。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "好，不动就不动。可是你为什么要怕我不要你？你难道不知道，就算用全世界的人来换你一个，我也不换的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "真的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "当然是真的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "若用那个水柔青来换呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "她的确是个很好的女孩子，而且很可怜，只可惜我心里早已经被你一个人占满了，再也容不下别的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "我知道你那么样做，是为了试试我，对你是不是忠心。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你若肯在那里留下来，这一辈子就休想再看见我了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "可是我已经到这里来了之后，你为什么还不让我来见你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "因为还有别的人也要试试你，看你是不是够聪明、够胆量，看你的心是不是够好，够不够资格做我爹爹的女婿。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "所以他们就看我是不是够聪明能找出这间屋子的秘密，是不是够胆量到龙王庙去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "在那龙王庙里，你若是敢动我那小表妹的坏主意，或是不肯先送她回来，你就算能找到这里，还是看不见我的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "幸亏我是个又聪明、又有胆量的大好人……",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "否则你又怎么能娶到这么好的老婆呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "到现在我才发现我们真是天生的一对。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你现在才发现？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "因为我现在才发现，我们两个人的脸皮都够厚的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "好热的天气，王老大想必更懒得动了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "这些日子来，他和小林不知道在干什么。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你放心，他们绝不会寂寞的，尤其是小林。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你难道忘记了那个卖花的小姑娘？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "你莫要忘记你现在身上穿的是什么衣服？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "没关系，反正我就算不唱，别人也一样能看出我是个女人的，一个女人要扮得像男人，并不是件容易事。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "你以前呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "以前不同。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "有什么不同？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "以前我比较脏……很脏，大家都觉得女人总应该比男人干净。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "其实呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "其实女人本来就比男人干净。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王老大和小林若知道我们……我们已经成为夫妻，一定也会很高兴的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "不知道小林会不会吃醋。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "我爹爹自己现在虽不能喝酒了，却很喜欢看别人喝。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "他以前的酒量一定也不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "何止不错，十个郭大路也未必能喝得过他一个。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "哈。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "哈是什么意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "哈的意思就是我非但不服气，而且不相信。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "只可惜他现在老了，而且旧伤复发，已有多年躺在床上不能动，否则他不把你灌得满地乱爬才怪。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "他实在是个很了不起的人，我想不到他会让我们走的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "因为……因为他实在太寂寞，若是换了别人，一定会要我们陪着他。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "可是他不同，他从不愿为了自己让别人痛苦，无论多么难以忍受的事，他都宁可一个人独自忍受。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "说老实话，我从来也没有想到他是个这样子的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "从前你以为他是什么样的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "你知道，江湖中的传说，将他说得多么可怕。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "现在呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "现在我才知道，江湖中的那些传说才真正可怕，他居然能忍受了这么多年，就凭这一点，已不是别人能比得上的了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "这也许只因为他已没法不忍受。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "幸好他还有朋友，我看到神驼子他们对他的忠实和友情，总忍不住要替他觉得欢喜感动。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你知不知道他们以前是想怎么对付他的？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "他们以前也是一心想要来杀他的，可是后来，经过了几次生死缠斗之后，他们才发现他并不是传说中那样的人，也被他的人格所感动，所以才成了他的朋友。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "为了他，金罗汉甚至不惜背叛了少林，不惜做一个终生再也见不得天日的叛徒。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "人岂非也就因为有这种伟大的感情，所以才和畜生不同。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "这种感情也惟有在生死患难之中，才能显得出它的伟大来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是你？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "妇人",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你走，我不认得你。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "你怎会变成这样子的？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "妇人",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "那是我的事，和你没关系。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "这是你跟他生的么？他的人呢？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "妇人",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "他骗了我，骗去了我的私房钱，又和别的女人跑了，却将这两个孽种留下来给我，我为什么这么苦命……为什么？",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "你已知道她是谁了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "她既然是你的朋友，你就应该尽力帮助她。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "妇人",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "你是什么人？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "我是他的妻子。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "妇人",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你已经成了亲？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "妇人",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你本来要娶我的，怎么能和别人成亲？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "是你离开了他，不是他不要你，以前的事你自己也该记得的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "妇人",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "我记得什么？我只记得他曾经告诉过我，他永远只喜欢我一个人，除了我之外，他绝不再娶别的女人。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "妇人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是他却骗了我，骗了我这个苦命的女人，你们大家来评评理……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "他并没有骗你，从来也没有骗过你，只可惜你已不是以前那个人了，你自己也该明白。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "妇人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我什么都不明白，我不想活了……我就是死也要跟这狠心的男人死在一起。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "你认不认得这是什么？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "妇人",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "我当然认得，这本来也是我的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "所以我现在还给你。只不过希望你知道，为了保存这条金链子，他不惜挨饿挨骂，甚至不惜被朋友耻笑——他这是为了什么，你也该想得到的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "你换了这条金链子，已可好好的做点小生意，好好的养你的孩子。以后你一定还会遇着好男人的，只要你不再欺骗别人，别人也不会来欺骗你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "莫忘记你已是母亲，已应该替你的孩子想一想，他将来也会长大的，你应该让他觉得，因为有你这样一个母亲而骄傲。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "妇人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老天……老天，你为什么又要让我看见他……为什么？",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "你什么时候将那金链子赎出来的？为什么不告诉我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "因为我根本就没有赎出来。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "你没有？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "刚才我给她的金链子，根本不是你的那条。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "不是？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "那是梅兰姐妹私下里送给我的贺礼。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "那你为什么要拿出来，为什么要这样做？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 582,
      "line_end": 582
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "因为我也是个女人，我对女人总比你了解得多。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "你是说她看到了这条金链子，就会想起我以前对她总算不错，所以才肯放过我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 588
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "金链子看起来都是差不多的，连你都已经分不清了，又何况她。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 590,
      "line_end": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "可是看到我的时候，就应该已经想起以前……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "她那样子对你，并不是为以前的事，而是因为嫉妒。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 604
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "嫉妒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 608
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "也不是嫉妒你，是嫉妒我。看看她自己的日子，再看看我们，她更悔恨自己以前为什么要那样做。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 610,
      "line_end": 612
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "一个人对自己悔恨的时候，往往就会莫名其妙的对别人也怀恨起来，恨不得全世界的人都和她一样痛苦。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "所以她就想破坏我们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 618,
      "line_end": 618
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "她恨你，只不过因为她知道自己已永远无法再得到你了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 620,
      "line_end": 620
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "可是她看到了那条金链子时，为什么忽然又变了呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 624,
      "line_end": 624
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "因为金链子和你不同。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 626,
      "line_end": 626
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "金链子不但比你好看，而且她知道自己一定可以得到。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 630
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "是不是因为金链子已经在她的手里了！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 632,
      "line_end": 632
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "答对了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 634,
      "line_end": 634
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "谢谢你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 646,
      "line_end": 648
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "谢谢我？……谢谢我那条金链子？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 650,
      "line_end": 650
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "你应该知道我谢的是什么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 652
    }
